    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## get_news_v2 改进说明\n\n**相比 v1 的优化：**\n1. Firecrawl → Jina AI Reader（免费额度 100万 tokens/月）\n2. 移除 SplitInBatches 循环（利用 n8n 原生多 item 处理）\n3. LLM 批量评分（Gemini 2.5 Flash，HTTP Request 直调 + thinking 禁用）\n4. 日期过滤集成在 Build scoring prompt 中（最近3天）\n5. 新增内容截断（>12000字符防止 LLM 报错）\n6. 新增内容空值检查（跳过抓取失败的文章）\n7. LLM 评分失败时自动降级为关键词评分 fallback\n\n**导入后需配置凭证：**\n- Jina AI Reader → 选择已有 Jina AI account\n- Gemini API Key → 新建 Query Auth 凭证（Name: key, Value: 你的 Gemini API Key）\n- Google Gemini → 选择已有 Gemini API 凭证（摘要节点）\n- Feishu → 选择已有 Feishu account",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 4
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1140,
        160
      ],
      "id": "57626e0c-3c51-4d51-acdc-14e0f6548490",
      "name": "Sticky Note"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const allItems = $input.all();\n\n// Filter: only keep articles from the last 3 days\nconst now = new Date();\nconst cutoff = new Date(now.getTime() - 3 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000);\nconst items = allItems.filter(item => {\n  const pubDate = new Date(item.json.pubDate);\n  return !isNaN(pubDate.getTime()) && pubDate >= cutoff && pubDate <= now;\n});\n\nif (items.length === 0) return [];\n\nconst titles = items.map((item, i) =>\n  `${i + 1}. ${item.json.title || 'Untitled'}`\n).join('\\n');\n\nconst prompt = `你是AI新闻编辑。以下是今日RSS聚合的${items.length}条新闻标题。\n请为每条评分(1-10)并识别重复新闻。\n\n评分标准：\n- 重大产品发布/技术突破/开源发布: 8-10\n- 重要行业动态/融资/合作/政策: 5-7\n- 一般技术讨论/教程/评测: 3-4\n- 旧闻/水文/广告/招聘: 1-2\n\n对于内容相同的重复新闻（不同来源报道同一事件），只在最佳标题上给分，其余标记dup为true。\n\n严格以JSON数组返回，不要包含其他文字：\n[{\"index\":1,\"score\":8,\"dup\":false},{\"index\":2,\"score\":3,\"dup\":true},...]\n\n标题列表：\n${titles}`;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    prompt,\n    originalItems: items.map(item => item.json)\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        -180,
        380
      ],
      "id": "aa11bb22-cc33-dd44-ee55-ff6677889900",
      "name": "Build scoring prompt"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/gemini-2.5-flash-lite:generateContent",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpQueryAuth",
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={{ JSON.stringify({ contents: [{ role: \"user\", parts: [{ text: $json.prompt }] }], generationConfig: { thinkingConfig: { thinkingBudget: 0 } } }) }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        60,
        380
      ],
      "id": "bb22cc33-dd44-ee55-ff66-778899001122",
      "name": "LLM Score",
      "credentials": {
        "httpQueryAuth": {
          "id": "",
          "name": "Gemini API Key"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Extract text from Gemini API response\nlet llmText = '';\nif ($json.candidates && $json.candidates[0] && $json.candidates[0].content) {\n  llmText = $json.candidates[0].content.parts.filter(p => p.text).map(p => p.text).join('');\n} else {\n  llmText = $json.text || '';\n}\nconst originalItems = $('Build scoring prompt').first().json.originalItems;\n\ntry {\n  // 提取 JSON 数组（容忍 LLM 输出中的额外文字）\n  const jsonMatch = llmText.match(/\\[[\\s\\S]*\\]/);\n  if (!jsonMatch) throw new Error('No JSON array found in LLM response');\n\n  const scores = JSON.parse(jsonMatch[0]);\n\n  // 过滤重复、按分数排序、取 Top 15\n  const ranked = scores\n    .filter(s => !s.dup && s.score >= 3)\n    .sort((a, b) => b.score - a.score)\n    .slice(0, 15)\n    .map(s => ({ json: originalItems[s.index - 1] }))\n    .filter(item => item.json);  // 安全校验\n\n  if (ranked.length === 0) throw new Error('No valid items after parsing');\n  return ranked;\n\n} catch (e) {\n  // ===== FALLBACK: 关键词评分（当前方案） =====\n  const keywords = {\n    'launch': 3, 'release': 3, 'announce': 3, 'unveil': 3,\n    'breakthrough': 3, 'open-source': 3, 'opensource': 3,\n    'gpt': 2, 'claude': 2, 'gemini': 2, 'llama': 2, 'mistral': 2,\n    'openai': 2, 'anthropic': 2, 'deepseek': 2, 'nvidia': 2,\n    'agent': 2, 'multimodal': 2, 'reasoning': 2, 'agi': 2,\n    'benchmark': 1, 'performance': 1, 'training': 1, 'inference': 1,\n    'regulation': 1, 'safety': 1, 'alignment': 1, 'robotics': 1,\n    'autonomous': 1, 'transformer': 1, 'fine-tun': 1, 'dataset': 1\n  };\n  const scored = originalItems.map((json, i) => {\n    const title = (json.title || '').toLowerCase();\n    let score = 0;\n    for (const [kw, pts] of Object.entries(keywords)) {\n      if (title.includes(kw)) score += pts;\n    }\n    return { json, score, titleKey: title.split(/\\s+/).slice(0,5).join(' ') };\n  });\n  const seen = new Set();\n  const deduped = scored.filter(e => {\n    if (seen.has(e.titleKey)) return false;\n    seen.add(e.titleKey);\n    return true;\n  });\n  deduped.sort((a, b) => b.score - a.score);\n  return deduped.slice(0, 15).map(e => ({ json: e.json }));\n}"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        300,
        380
